                        base="i1057715"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-13</xref>, Notice of Set-Aside of Orders, in solicitations and contracts to notify offerors if an order or orders are to be set aside for any of the small business concerns identified in <xref href="FAR-i1101771.dita#i1101771"
                        base="i1101771"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.000</xref>(a)(3).</p>
